{"tid":1566853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚冇去金鐘嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2019-09-13T18:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T17:42:26.000Z","uid":269091,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90fb133c85cee38037968578a038cd81fa5765bf","tid":1566853,"uid":269091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T18:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcN0MmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcN0MmC.jpg&h=6468faa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n今日中秋佳節理應喜氣洋洋，又或各位會選擇到各大公園及太平獅子兩山會師高唱國歌，本預是日參與人數只數百寮寮，但卻前後逾千市民流水式拜祭諸位義士，連儂牆公祭區籌委會手足仝人特此感謝來到悼念的同路人，感謝身處其他地方為義士默哀的戰友，更感謝到收押所聲援的手足。<br />\n<br />\n香港人只有眼前路，沒有身後身，我們必須繼承義士遺願，戰鬥到底。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公祭區未知何時會被清場，如欲前往拜祭者請盡快到現場悼念。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n連儂牆公祭區籌委會<br />\n<br />\n9月13日"},{"pid":"34bc6e3ae2309ce8e477753aa9724161aa3aa1ff","tid":1566853,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8282588c9fcb68641bb24ddf42b49b83f854c0b6","tid":1566853,"uid":269091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"P牌 推唔到"},{"pid":"45f10bf5987d8c71a02b2e1abdc69f19630a0ee1","tid":1566853,"uid":269091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:15:04.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"eccff734b21363283ffedd0bbda56d21149d7010","tid":1566853,"uid":79453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:29:33.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af12c5766c3099478ab17681b548188404d70226","tid":1566853,"uid":171087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T19:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa